headline: TD Cowen lowers PVH rating to Hold on structural risks, shares down
summary: Investing.com -- PVH (NYSE:PVH) shares slid 1.7% in premarket trading Wednesday after TD Cowen lowered the rating on the stock to Hold and the price target to $74, citing intensifying competition, rising tariffs, and weakening wholesale data as structural risks to the business.
